attachment.title:
👇🏼Save & share these spots and itineraries ⬇️

📍Cinder Cone (Lassen Volcanic NP)
📍Artists Palette (Death Valley NP)
📍Congress Trail (Sequoia NP)
📍Bald Rock Dome (Butte County)
📍Grove of Titans (Redwoods NP)
📍Subway Cave Lava Tubes
📍Lake Shasta Caverns

👇🏼Here are road trip guides that go to these spots 

🌋 Road Trip 1: Lassen Vocanic 
1. Lake Helen
2. Cinder Cone ⭐️
3. Manzanita Lake
4. Chaos Crags
5. Kings Creek Falls
6. Bumpass Hell
7. Burney Falls
8. McCloud Falls
9. Castle Crags
10. Hedge Creek Falls
11. Castle Lake
12. Lake Siskiyou
13. Shasta Caverns

🌲 Road Trip 2: Redwoods 
1. Jedediah Smith
2. Grove of Titans ⭐️
3. Humboldt Redwoods SP
4. Tall Trees Grove
5. Avenue of the Giants

🌳Road Trip 3: Sequoia 
1. Tunnel Log 
2. The President Tree 
3. The Senate (Congress Trail)⭐️
4. Moro Rock
5. Tokopah Falls
6. Big Trees Trail
7. Parker Group Sequoias 
8. General Sherman 
9. General Grant 
10. Hume Lake 

🏴‍☠️ Road Trip 4: Death Valley 
1. Artists Palette ⭐️
2. Zabriskie Point
3. Badwater Basin
4. Mesquite Flat Sand Dunes
5. Golden Canyon to Red Cathedral
6. Dante’s View
7. Sidewinder Canyon 

Follow @alexkhachigian for more tips, itineraries, and adventures ✨

#visitcalifornia #california #californiaroadtrip #usaroadtrip #californiaadventure
